Subject: Task Frame Launch Queue Event

Description: Inspectable launch queue for task-frame worker candidates.

& [TaskFrameLaunchQueue:lmstudio_task_frame_launch_queue_20260624_001] is a task-frame launch queue
  + [queue_id] is lmstudio_task_frame_launch_queue_20260624_001
  + [queue_status] is ready_for_inspection
  + [candidate_count] is 1
  + [ready_count] is 1
  + [blocked_count] is 0
  + [launch_policy] is inspect_before_launch; no_silent_launch
  + [created_utc] is 2026-06-24T19:45:29Z
  + [outside] is automatic launch, worker mutation authority, hidden model state, unrelated dirty files
  = must: keep Codex as launch, validation, and integration authority
  = must: keep ready candidates inspectable before launch
  - never: launch silently from queue readiness

& [TaskFrameLaunchCandidate:lmstudio_next_probe_001] is a queued task-frame launch candidate
  + [candidate_id] is lmstudio_next_probe_001
  + [task_frame_id] is task_frame_lmstudio_next_probe_001
